    <h1 class="page-title">Travelling Course — <em>English A1</em></h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Survival English for travel. From your first hello at the airport to navigating a foreign city with confidence — all the real-world language you need from day one abroad.</p>
    <div class="level-pill">✈️ Level A1 · 10 units · 50 lessons</div>
  </header>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-val">10</div><div class="stat-lbl">Units</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-val">50</div><div class="stat-lbl">Lessons</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-val">~50h</div><div class="stat-lbl">Total time</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-val">200+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Travel phrases</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-val">10</div><div class="stat-lbl">Real scenarios</div></div>
  </div>
