    <strong>Every lesson is a real travel situation.</strong> Vocabulary and grammar from earlier units are recycled in every new scenario — so students don't just learn words, they practise using them in increasingly complex, realistic situations. The ↻ symbol shows exactly what earlier material is reactivated and how.
